tte Black", bulletpointTwo: "• Manufacturer: Flextronics, Foxconn", bulletpointThree: "• CPU: 3.8 GHz custom AMD Zen 2 (8 core)",bulletpointFour: "• GPU: 1825 MHz AMD Custom RDNA 2",bulletpointFive:"• Memory: 16 GB GDDR6", bulletpointSix: "• Hard Drive: 1TB", bulletpointSeven: "• Media: CD, DVD, Blu-Ray, 4K UHD", bulletpointEight: "• Video Output: HDMI (up to 8K support)", bulletpointNine: "• Network: Gigabit Ethernet, Wifi", bulletpointTen: "• Audio: 7.1 Surround Sound", bulletpointEleven: "• Code Name: Anaconda", bulletpointTwelve: " "),
            
